Subject: [PATCH v2 2/6] i2c: iproc: handle only slave interrupts which are enabled
Date:   Fri, 30 Oct 2020 12:23:35 +0530
Message-Id: <20201030065339.955-3-rayagonda.kokatanur@broadcom.com>
